# Normalise line endings: the code runs in a Linux Docker image, so store text
# as LF in the repo regardless of the host OS. Keeps diffs clean cross-platform.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets the pipeline may produce — never normalise these.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.mp3 binary
*.wav binary
*.mp4 binary
*.ts  binary
